	(40, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'service', '{"category_id":"1","name":"SaaS Architecture","model":"Botble\\\\Portfolio\\\\Models\\\\Service","slug":"saas-architecture","slug_id":"38","is_slug_editable":"1","description":"Designing and building scalable, multi-product SaaS ecosystems from concept to launch, focusing on high-impact, robust solutions","content":"<p>As a SaaS Architect and Innovation Leader, I specialize in transforming complex challenges into scalable, high-impact technology solutions. My approach combines deep expertise in full-stack development with strategic product management to design and launch cutting-edge products that drive business growth and enhance user experience.<\\/p><p>My career is highlighted by the successful architecture and launch of a comprehensive SaaS ecosystem for a pioneering UK-based AI and cloud solutions provider. This expansive ecosystem features more than nine specialized, AI-driven products designed to serve multiple business verticals.<\\/p><p>Key platforms developed within this SaaS architecture include:<\\/p><ul style=\\"list-style-type:disc;\\"><li style=\\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\\"><strong>KP Learn:<\\/strong> An online course marketplace built with Flutter, Laravel, and Firebase.<\\/li><li style=\\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\\"><strong>KP Commerce:<\\/strong> A multi-vendor eCommerce platform for both digital and physical goods.<\\/li><li style=\\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\\"><strong>KP Task:<\\/strong> A project management and team collaboration platform utilizing Flutter, Laravel, and Vue.js.<\\/li><li style=\\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\\"><strong>KP HRM:<\\/strong> A complete human resource and payroll management system.<\\/li><li style=\\"tab-stops:list 36.0pt;\\"><strong>AI-Driven Applications:<\\/strong> Innovative solutions such as \\"Sleepy Owl Stories,\\" an AI-powered storytelling app, and \\"Pocket Chef AI,\\" an AI cooking assistant.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>The technological foundation for these SaaS products consists of a robust stack including Laravel, Vue.js, Flutter, PHP, MySQL, and Firebase. This expertise allows me to architect and deliver a cohesive suite of intelligent applications tailored to specific business needs.<\\/p>","seo_meta":{"seo_title":null,"seo_description":null,"index":"index"},"seo_meta_image":null,"status":"published","is_featured":"1","order":"0","image":null,"icon":"ti ti-database","submitter":"apply"}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/138.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', '127.0.0.1', 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 6, 'SaaS Architecture', 'primary', '2025-08-06 23:21:59', '2025-08-06 23:21:59'),
	(41, 1, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', 'service', '{"category_id":"3","name":"Full-Stack Development","model":"Botble\\\\Portfolio\\\\Models\\\\Service","slug":"cloud-integration","slug_id":"37","is_slug_editable":"1","description":"Crafting end-to-end web solutions using modern frameworks like Laravel, Vue.js, and Node.js for seamless and powerful applications.","content":"<p>My expertise as a Full-Stack Developer involves crafting complete, end-to-end web and mobile solutions, from initial ideation and architecture to final deployment. This holistic approach ensures the delivery of seamless and powerful applications designed to meet complex business requirements.<\\/p><p>My capabilities are built on a strong foundation in both backend and frontend technologies, with a 90% proficiency rating in Web &amp; Backend development.<\\/p><p><strong>Backend Development:<\\/strong> My primary backend expertise lies in using the Laravel framework with PHP to build robust and scalable server-side logic. I have successfully used Laravel to develop an entire SaaS ecosystem of over nine products, including platforms for eCommerce, HR management, and project management. My skills also extend to Node.js. I am proficient in designing and implementing both REST APIs and GraphQL to ensure efficient data communication. For databases, I have extensive experience with both relational (MySQL) and non-relational (MongoDB, Firebase) systems.<\\/p><p><strong>Frontend Development:<\\/strong> On the frontend, I create dynamic and interactive user interfaces using modern JavaScript frameworks like Vue.js and React.js. This was practically applied in projects like KP Task, a project management platform where I utilized Vue.js for the frontend in conjunction with a Laravel backend. My experience as a startup founder also involved developing websites and UX\\/UI solutions for multiple clients, honing my skills in creating user-centric designs.<\\/p>","seo_meta":{"seo_title":null,"seo_description":n