	(3, 'Elite', 'Enterprise-grade apps with AI, advanced features, and long-term collaboration.', NULL, '129', NULL, 'hourly', 'Custom architecture, no design assets needed\r\nSaaS platform design + development (multi-role, subscription, cloud scaling)\r\nAI integrations (GPT, TTS, OCR, image recognition)\r\nFinTech-grade security (root detection, OTP, encryption)\r\nCI/CD pipeline setup, Docker, AWS/GCP deployment\r\n🔁 Weekly strategy & progress calls\r\n🔧 12 months of dedicated post-launch support\r\n🎁 VIP onboarding kit, performance optimization, and care package\r\n👥 Ideal for enterprise clients, long-term product builds, or funded startups', 'published', 0, 'Get Started', '/contact', '2025-08-07 00:29:43', '2025-08-07 00:31:43', 2);

